      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget ride or a hands-on project? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has significant wear both inside and out, and will require mechanical attention to get it running reliably. That said, it's a real opportunity for the mechanically savvy buyer or someone who just needs basic transportation and isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves. At this price point, you're getting a chance to own a vehicle with serious upside potential if you're willing to put in the work!",
