      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, functional ride that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it has some wear and imperfections that go beyond everyday use, but it's still a capable vehicle with plenty of miles left to give. Priced to reflect its honest condition, this is a great opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer who wants dependable transportation without the premium price tag. What you see is what you get \u2014 straightforward, no surprises!",
