    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and the price has been set honestly to reflect its current state \u2014 please read the full description carefully before reaching out. The car does run, but it requires significant attention: it has noticeable mechanical issues that will need addressing, visible body damage including rust and dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional components. This is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks involved. There are no warranties implied or offered, and we strongly encourage an inspection before purchase. What you see is what you get \u2014 we believe in full transparency so there are no surprises after the sale.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and we want buyers to have a realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows visible wear \u2014 you can expect some scratches, minor dents, and paint fading in certain areas, though the body is structurally sound. The interior is functional but shows signs of use, including worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim pieces, and general aging consistent with a well-used vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid option for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind putting a little work into a vehicle, priced fairly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 a truly exceptional find in the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains its deep, original luster and bodywork completely free of dents, scratches, or blemishes. The interior is equally impressive, showing no signs of wear on the seats, carpets, dashboard, or trim \u2014 it presents as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights or known issues of any kind. The tires have excellent tread remaining, all glass is clear and chip-free, and every electronic feature operates perfectly. This is the kind of used car that is genuinely hard to find \u2014 one where you can buy with complete confidence and drive away without a single reservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
